        <section id="fs-id3260705" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problems &amp; Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-id3063257" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id3175132">        <para id="import-auto-id1576722">What is the repulsive force between two pith balls that are 8.00 cm apart and have equal charges of – 30.0 nC?</para>
