            <exercise id="fs-id1861080" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1389499">        <para id="import-auto-id1037692">(a) Find the ratio of the electrostatic to gravitational force between two electrons. (b) What is this ratio for two protons? (c) Why is the ratio different for electrons and protons?</para>
