<m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3.00 m</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> apart, and their total charge is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mi>µ</m:mi><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. (a) If the force of repulsion between them is 0.075N, what are magnitudes of the two charges? (b) If one charge attracts the other with a force of 0.525N, what are the magnitudes of the two charges? Note that you may need to solve a quadratic equation to reach your answer.</para></problem></exercise>
